Hello <%=@employee.name%>,

This email is to inform you that the <%= @meeting.title %> meeting has changed. The meeting details are now as follows:

    Title: <%= @meeting.title %>
    Room: <%= @meeting.room.name %> (<%= @meeting.room.room_number %>)
    Location: <%= @meeting.room.location %>
    Start Time: <%= @meeting.start_time.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M%P") %>
    End Time: <%= @meeting.end_time.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M%P") %>


Please be sure to arrive on time. Thank you.

Sincerely,
<%= @meeting.employee.company.name %> Management
